N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5304.3 - Duration of license

State Regulations

Casino key employee licenses shall remain valid for five
years, pursuant to Racing, Pari-Mutuel Wagering and Breeding Law section
1325(6). Notes
